items.badge_description: The community has spoken and the 2025 Brewery Madness Champion is none other than the legends at Tree House Brewing Company! When it comes to making beloved beers, nobody does it quite like Tree House and this makes them back-to-back champs of our annual Brewery Madness tournament. This badge celebrates their 2025 Brewery Madness victory!
Are you crazy? Five different types of beer in one day? Hope you were just sampling.
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 5 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 2! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 5 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 2!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 20 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 5.

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 330 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 67!
